<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dr-satyr" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dr-satyr" class="zg-link" title="唐平">唐平</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
